  "prompt": "What is the meaning of sending nudge in hike messenger?",
  "response": "In the context of Hike Messenger, a \"nudge\" is a feature designed to remind or prompt someone to respond to a message or interact within a chat. It's essentially a gentle reminder that allows users to bring attention to a conversation that may have gone unnoticed or is lingering without a reply. Nudging can help keep conversations active and engaged, especially in group chats where multiple messages can easily lead to some being overlooked. This feature aims to enhance communication and ensure meaningful interactions among users.",
